Subject: Secunia Research: Microsoft Office FlashPix Property Set Parsing Buffer Overflow

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 14/12/2010

  - Microsoft Office FlashPix Property Set Parsing Buffer Overflow -

====================================================================== 
